Compiler-precise Scala code intelligence

Usage: kodex [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  index       Build kodex.idx from a compiled project's `SemanticDB` and Mill metadata
  search      Search for symbol definitions
  info        Complete picture of a type or method (members + callers + callees + related)
  calls       Call tree: downstream (default) or upstream (--reverse)
  noise       Detect noise candidates for --exclude patterns
  help        Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --idx <IDX>  Path to kodex.idx (default: .scalex/kodex.idx, or `KODEX_IDX` env var)
  -h, --help       Print help
  -V, --version    Print version